reviewText:
Product is described and pictured as a CD plus a DVD.  Product is actually a CD plus a Blu-Ray disc.  The Blu-Ray disc will not play in a DVD player.  I had already purchased the CD of this performance and bought this because I wanted a DVD of the performance and the price appeared to be very low.  So, this product was useless to me and a waste of money.

Considered returning the item. BUT IT COST MORE TO RETURN THE ITEM FOR A REFUND THAN WHAT I ORIGINALLY PAID FOR THE ITEM.  AMAZON IF YOU ARE LISTENING PLEASE CREDIT MY ACCOUNT.
I already reviewed the DVD only version of this so I'll go read that one but I had to give it five stars just love this band
I love the DVD and CD.  I watched this on Iowa Public Television and had to have it.  We are ordering more for family members. Would tell everyone this is the best.
